Interface ResourceReference

All Known Implementing Classes:
ConstantResourceReference, FsfwDefaultReference, ResourceDirectory
public interface ResourceReference

This interface can be understood as the dual interface to ResourceDependent. While the ResourceDependent publishes its need for certain resources, the ResourceReference can be used to provide a (potentially dynamic) path reference to these resources.

Author:
Simon Hampe
